{"tid":1320804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[純推測]速龍小隊出動時已經改為穿一般PTU警服","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T03:04:54.000Z","uid":64841,"like":386,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"dffefb6eb038e5d861e6ff35b86ba81fad5a3f18","tid":1320804,"uid":64841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"首先沙田同上水一戰, 係唔太見有平時身穿全藍色制服ge速龍小隊(特別戰術小隊), 即係下面張相件制服.<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2976761/org/69b6f225b7bd92ae7cbb0690ada4a058.jpg/YkI-7AlbXzJxsnMvPIjHwvIOunLcihwKLUgRrQdIEa0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2976761%2Forg%2F69b6f225b7bd92ae7cbb0690ada4a058.jpg%2FYkI-7AlbXzJxsnMvPIjHwvIOunLcihwKLUgRrQdIEa0&h=cc020956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但同時今日新聞有講琴日拗斷義士手腕ge狗係鄭柏林, 佢而家係警察機動部隊教官, 即係有好大機會係平時速龍小隊ge一員. 但佢當時只係身穿一般PTU警服,如下圖所示<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190715/large/1563168111_3c1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190715%2Flarge%2F1563168111_3c1a.jpg&h=9b75db6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋琴日現場好易發覺到經常有一小隊幾隻狗特別癲同特別兇死, 而且通常都係跑最前, 做法就好似平時速龍小隊突然衝前嚇退示威者, 但而家佢地換左一般制服 等義士戒心放低, 再衝上去狂用警棍亂打, 同時警察同政府又可以係形象上處於道德高地 等一般市民有錯覺以為班狗冇咁狼, 但狗始終都係狗, 獸性係收唔埋, <br />\n<br />\n偽裝後速龍小隊, 有別於一般PTU 佢地頭盔只係用半罩式(冇護後頸),而且通常會配戴護目鏡<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190715/large/1563126067_8f4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190715%2Flarge%2F1563126067_8f4c.jpg&h=5cbafa16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下圖右手面白衫3隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3032354/org/d26957b1d35a51e1d4a4f05a3c05ec28.jpg/ExhRJgPcb0CUPoPqXcWvkoZhQ2yDV0suBlDaeSxQ2nk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3032354%2Forg%2Fd26957b1d35a51e1d4a4f05a3c05ec28.jpg%2FExhRJgPcb0CUPoPqXcWvkoZhQ2yDV0suBlDaeSxQ2nk&h=af4ccb81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a05c1bf4c481f939482ede0a32ff34d7c37629a0","tid":1320804,"uid":64841,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"發夢時見到依班狗要更加小心"},{"pid":"2a70261323274a1eafa57ab33ba17792f5e9c267","tid":1320804,"uid":267172,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0b509536cde350687a54670750be2d4c4a7f8f","tid":1320804,"uid":3571,"like":195,"dislike":0,"score":195,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e64d6a2ffb218f8929a1d35dc89bcfde92e82851","tid":1320804,"uid":28170,"like":104,"dislike":0,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"證都唔帶,佢地邊個打邊個你都無可能分到,有軍人都無人知"},{"pid":"91c549936769e850ae9ceaac97f8630e3303c01e","tid":1320804,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44567b1ece5d09c9b55712b6f9833f715b0adcf4","tid":1320804,"uid":19842,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"應該係啦<br />\n上水個陣已經有 跳橋個個位有個都係帶呢D眼罩 <br />\n睇落身形都係fit d"},{"pid":"e49bb3bf7debae819bfc4dc7f9f5b784f57614d4","tid":1320804,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1204801289bb0c056764227f348ba0fb90df9cac","tid":1320804,"uid":261505,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"睇頭盔就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOps-core high cut helmet"},{"pid":"85135611092f428de7f5ce7b89c2b689de48c189","tid":1320804,"uid":63950,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f7467732eb07e51614